export function ClassNames(cls, mods, anotherClasses){

    console.log(Object.entries(mods).filter((className, value) => Boolean(value)))

    
    return [
        cls,
        ...anotherClasses,
        ...Object.entries(mods)
            .filter((className, value) => Boolean(value))
            .map((className) => className)


    ].join(' ')
}


console.log(ClassNames('app', {'selected': true}, ['qwe']))
